      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "THINKING OF YOU (2) took advantage of a low draw last start with an all-the-way win (19.57) at this track in a Grade 5 over 342m. The form out of her last race has been franked. Can measure up again. JAZZY BOO (5) boasts a strong record this journey with 13 wins and six minors from 30 tries. Comes off a (17.61) win last time, scoring by 2.25 lengths in a Other over 305m at Mt Gambier. With even luck and a clean start can sneak into the finish. HAYDEN'S MILK (1) missed the frame and was safely held latest finishing 6th at Murray Bridge Straight following on from a second place finish (16.75) there the start prior. Form here at the trip sound including three wins. Some good form is emerging from her last run. A forward showing wouldn't surprise.",
